BEGIN_PGML
Solve the system of equations using substitution.

[`\newcommand{\amp}{&}\left\{
                  \begin{alignedat}{4}
                  \amp [$left[0]] = [$right[0]] \\
                  \amp [$left[1]] = [$right[1]]
                  \end{alignedat}
                  \right.
                `]

[@KeyboardInstructions('Write each solution in [|variable = number|]* format.')@]**

[_]{$answer}{16}

[_]{$string}{16}

END_PGML

